753
00:56:51,697 --> 00:56:56,999
No, I forgot it. I ended up leaving it here.
So, you know.

754
00:56:57,103 --> 00:56:59,469
Yeah, well, you missed
a hell of a dorm party on Saturday.

755
00:56:59,572 --> 00:57:00,800
Oh, yeah?

756
00:57:00,906 --> 00:57:03,136
We almost had a girl there.

