796
00:59:40,397 --> 00:59:43,855
So, what does he think about what you do?
Does he know?

797
00:59:44,435 --> 00:59:46,596
Oh, no, he's long gone, Ben.

798
00:59:49,173 --> 00:59:50,970
My dad's gone, too.

799
01:00:03,921 --> 01:00:08,221
So, you know, when you came into the store
to ask me to join the team,

