01:00:33,616 --> 01:00:37,780
That is why you're on the team.
And that's why I came into the store.

808
01:00:38,988 --> 01:00:40,922
No, no, not so much...

809
01:00:41,023 --> 01:00:43,890
- Oh, God. I'm so, so sorry.
