01:05:38,316 --> 01:05:41,376
I still think there're bigger fish
to fry out there.

880
01:05:41,486 --> 01:05:42,817
So do I.

881
01:05:50,695 --> 01:05:52,287
Hey, Fisher.

882
01:05:52,397 --> 01:05:54,456
