883
01:05:54,566 --> 01:05:57,057
But don't worry.
Greatness evokes that reaction sometimes.

884
01:05:57,169 --> 01:06:00,104
- Don't worry about it. I gotta go.
- All right.

885
01:06:08,979 --> 01:06:10,947
- Hey.
- What's going on?

886
01:06:12,183 --> 01:06:15,812
