I chose for my final paper.

887
01:06:15,920 --> 01:06:17,547
- That's bullshit, Ben.
- What?

888
01:06:17,655 --> 01:06:19,589
I know when you're lying,
I'm your best friend.

889
01:06:19,690 --> 01:06:21,715
At least I thought I was.

890
01:06:22,860 --> 01:06:24,452
Are you on drugs, Ben?

891
01:06:24,562 --> 01:06:26,496
Because there's a group that meets
at Simpson Hall on Saturdays.

892
01:06:26,597 --> 01:06:28,531
No, no. Cam, I'm not on drugs, okay?

893
01:06:28,632 --> 01:06:31,396
