897
01:06:42,513 --> 01:06:44,174
What about Harvard?

898
01:06:45,649 --> 01:06:48,311
It'll find a way of working itself out.

899
01:06:49,019 --> 01:06:51,613
Look, I gotta go. I'll see you.

900
01:07:03,901 --> 01:07:07,997
<i>I think the worst part of it
was not being able to tell anyone.</i>

901
01:07:12,176 --> 01:07:16,305
<i>But for the first time in my life,
the world made itself easy for me.</i>

902
01:07:17,947 --> 01:07:19,073
Here you go, sir.

903
01:07:19,182 --> 01:07:20,740
<i>And I liked it.</i>

