01:07:29,626 --> 01:07:30,684
Yes.

907
01:07:30,793 --> 01:07:33,284
Now, Ben, this is how we play!

908
01:07:35,932 --> 01:07:38,366
<i>And play we did.</i>

909
01:07:42,605 --> 01:07:44,698
<i>Nothing cost too much.</i>

910
01:07:44,807 --> 01:07:47,332
<i>Nothing was out of reach.</i>

911
01:07:52,982 --> 01:07:55,815
<i>I guess you could say
the casino host of fate</i>

912
01:07:55,919 --> 01:07:58,513
<i>gave Ben Campbell a major upgrade.</i>

