920
01:09:31,146 --> 01:09:33,512
What line of work you in, mister?

921
01:09:34,249 --> 01:09:36,011
I count things.

922
01:09:38,185 --> 01:09:39,777
My name's Sierra.

923
01:09:40,354 --> 01:09:45,587
Hi, Sierra. I'm Salvador Sanchez.

924
01:09:47,595 --> 01:09:50,359
